name: Tokyo Metro's Ginza Line in English
description:
Ueno, Shibuya, Asakusa ... ever wondered what these famous place names in Tokyo mean?

Wonder no more! This stylish poster presents all the station names along Tokyo Metro's Ginza Line in English. Hop on for a jocular ride along the winding tracks of cross-cultural semantics!

If you are infatuated with Japanese culture, love riding the Tokyo Metro, appreciate minimalist design, or simply like to make your peers green with envy by adding a tasteful accent to your collection —— this poster is for you!

format: PNG
resolution: 3500×2500
artist: Issey Fujishima 
location: Jakarta, 2021
